UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 1841
1 (b) All hemp-derived vapor product containers shipped or delivered to a
2 consumer shall be conspicuously labeled with the words: "CONTAINS
3 HEMP-DERIVED VAPOR PRODUCTS: SIGNATURE OF PERSON AGE
4 21 OR OLDER REQUIRED FOR DELIVERY".
5 (3) At the time of delivery, the recipient of the shipment or delivery shall present to
6 the individual delivering the package a valid identification document. Prior to
7 transferring possession of the package, the individual delivering the package
8 shall visually inspect the document and verify the identity of the recipient and, by
9 visual examination or by using age verification technology, that the recipient is at
10 least twenty-one (21) years of age.
11 (4) Before transferring possession of the package, the individual delivering the
12 package shall obtain the signature of the recipient of the shipment or delivery.
13 The individual who receives and signs for the hemp-derived vapor product is not
14 required to be the consumer who purchased the hemp-derived vapor product.
15 (5) A retailer or common or private carrier that fails to comply with this section
16 shall:
17 (a) For the first offense, be guilty of a violation punishable by a fine of one
18 thousand five hundred dollars ($1,500); and
19 (b) For each subsequent offense, be guilty of a violation punishable by a fine of
20 three thousand dollars ($3,000).
21 (6) (a) A consumer who intentionally causes an unlawful shipment or delivery
22 under this section shall:
23 1. For the first offense, be guilty of a violation punishable by a fine of
24 seven hundred fifty dollars ($750); and
25 2. For each subsequent offense, be guilty of a violation punishable by a
26 fine of one thousand five hundred dollars ($1,500).
27 (b) The retailer and the common or private carrier shall not be liable for a
Page 2 of 3
